javadiptraceasciilib

Class DiptraceProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • javadiptraceasciilib.DiptraceProject

  • public final class DiptraceProject
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is holds a diptrace project. It can have both the schematics and the pcb.
